      "post_content": "You know, you don't need to mention Training Grounds on every single card that has a colorless activated ability.   \n  \nHere's a thought: Start saying [Heartstone](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Heartstone) instead. That way, the cost of Training Grounds won't go up one dollar every time a new player starts playing magic and learns about the Gatherer.",
